{"tid":1005650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京用「超級馬里奧」卡通作反腐宣傳涉侵權","createTime":"2019-02-02T11:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T19:30:48.000Z","uid":104257,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b2bb8b02db567b2ca57f8702d748298b10ba743a","tid":1005650,"uid":104257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:18:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">中共中央政法委員會推出新的反貪腐宣傳片，但涉嫌侵犯版權。<br />\n<br />\n片段模擬電視遊戲，法官闖關期間，老虎、蒼蠅一起打，表揚湖南法院去年嚴厲打擊職務犯罪，有超過一千名官員涉案，其中13人是正廳級以上的幹部，同時宣揚國家主席習近平的反貪腐政策。但片段的角色、場景，以至是背景音樂，都同日本任天堂的電視遊戲「超級馬里奧」一模一樣，涉嫌侵犯版權。片段現在已經下架，任天堂低調回應，指不會針對個別案件發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n北京政府的反貪腐宣傳過往多次使用「超級馬里奧」，但從未得到公司的授權。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=336386&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D336386%26refer%3D&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2QAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=e0710dd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D336386%26refer%3D&h=bc884fe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=336386&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"aebd86c6f5c3f9488714641bec04ea39017a4f46","tid":1005650,"uid":20449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:22:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3706a57a87d5ea94a14c62843bc4a3a40972ed9c","tid":1005650,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"等睇mario是支國原創的，日本是老翻的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9486a230360f5251c97bb94106ec03e1eebaaca2","tid":1005650,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:10:33.000Z","msg":"怕撚咩 係贏國"},{"pid":"5388484866ced866920c5e332d52f0d5fb0954f0","tid":1005650,"uid":39840,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:11:47.000Z","msg":"任天堂最強法務部都淆底唔敢告 <img 